A three-year-old girl was on Sunday electrocuted as she played at a church compound in Njiru area, Nairobi.The child was playing with her friends when she touched a naked live wire, killing her instantly.This is the sixth incident to be reported in the city in the past week.In a separate incident, a43-year-old man was found dead inside his house in Hurlingam area, Nairobi. The man is believed to have committed suicide by swallowing poison.